                                <div class="vc_row wpb_row vc_inner vc_row-fluid"><div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-md-6"><div class="vc_column-inner"><div class="wpb_wrapper">
                                                <div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element" >
                                                    <div class="wpb_wrapper">
                                                        <p class="faq_title"><strong>Do I need to pay a fee for the Reseller Program every year?</strong></p>
                                                        <p>No, you will only need to pay a one time fee of RM595 and you will be eligible to enjoy a 20% discount on all package prices.</p>

                                                    </div>
                                                </div>

                                                <div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element" >
                                                    <div class="wpb_wrapper">
                                                        <p class="faq_title"><strong>Can I use the templates images to promote the eCommerce packages?</strong></p>
                                                        <p>Resellers under the Reseller program are not allowed to use the templates images for any illustration or promotion purposes to adhere to copyright regulations.</p>

                                                    </div>
                                                </div>

                                                <div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element" >
                                                    <div class="wpb_wrapper">
                                                        <p class="faq_title"><strong>Is there any restriction on how much I can markup on Karobar’s reseller package price?</strong></p>
                                                        <p>No, there is no restriction. Furthermore, you may opt to enhance the value of the package that you plan to sell, by adding in your services and then markup the total package pricing to the amount you wish to sell at.</p>

                                                    </div>
                                                </div>

                                                <div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element" >
                                                    <div class="wpb_wrapper">
                                                        <p class="faq_title"><strong>Will my customer’s website be upgraded automatically when Karobar rolls out any new features or applies patches for bugs?</strong></p>
                                                        <p>Yes, your customers will receive the exact same updates as our customers do.</p>

                                                    </div>
                                                </div>
                                            </div></div></div><div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-md-6"><div class="vc_column-inner"><div class="wpb_wrapper">
                                                <div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element" >
                                                    <div class="wpb_wrapper">
                                                        <p class="faq_title"><strong>Can my customer upgrade their plan anytime?</strong></p>
                                                        <p>Yes, your customer can always start small and upgrade their plans whenever they like. You’ll only have to pay the price differences between the current plan and upgraded plan.</p>

                                                    </div>
                                                </div>

                                                <div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element" >
                                                    <div class="wpb_wrapper">
                                                        <p class="faq_title"><strong>What sort of support can I expect from SiteGiant?</strong></p>
                                                        <p>In the Reseller Program, we will not deal directly with your customers and stay completely invisible from your customers. We strongly advise that you go through our tutorial guide and provide 1st layer of support to your customers.</p>
                                                        <p>If you wish to opt for direct support, our support team will be available to provide professional assistance to your customers as well; however, do note that your customers may know of Karobar branding.</p>
                                                        <p>Should you or your customers have any question, feel free to reach out to our support team at support@karobar.my.</p>

                                                    </div>
                                                </div>

                                                <div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element" >
                                                    <div class="wpb_wrapper">
                                                        <p class="faq_title"><strong>I still have some unanswered questions, what should I do?</strong></p>
                                                        <p>Please do not hesitate to contact our Sales team at sales@karobar.my or call 012-719 0122.</p>

                                                    </div>
